<br>
Manuverability!<br>
<br>
Running through crowded hallways while being chased by big scary things.<br>
<br>
Ability to squeeze between bars in some &quot;jails&quot;.<br>
<br>
Ease of picking your way through a crowded raid to hand a stack of food or a damage bracer to a needy guildmate.<br>
